entries.d:
a. Of, pertaining to resembling, or containing, manganese;
specif., designating compounds in which manganese has a higher valence
as contrasted with manganous compounds. Cf. Manganous.

v. t. To make a matron of; to make matronlike.
v. t. To act the part of a marton toward; to superintend;
to chaperone; as, to matronize an assembly.
